Pre-Game Insights: Team India will play under Jasprit Bumrah who is making his comeback after one year.
The squad will also have fresh faces like Rinku Singh and Jitesh Sharma.
On the other hand, Shivam Dube, Prasidh Krishna, and Washington Sundar are set for their long-awaited comeback.
Miscellaneous Highlights: India faced Ireland for the first time in the shortest format in the 2009 T20 World Cup where India won the game by 8 wickets.
After this, India had two tours to Ireland (2018 and 2022) with 2-match T20 series and both of which were won by India.
